messages.text: where u at babe...i wanna see u.
uh, yes, yes, i just didn’t know u were gonna txt…
i told u i was yesterday… where r u??
where else?? my husband isn’t home.
where did ur husband say he would be?
some bar. u know how drunk he gets, will be out all night
y all the questions?? usually u would be begging to come at this point
ya, im fine. this was just, unexpected.
u sure?? cause usually its out of the blue like this
u know i hate that word
jus get over here and stop actin weird
askin all these questions...plus ur txtin style is different…
jus abbreviating everything, usually real formal
have u every wondered whether or not this is hurting Dave?
wat?? wat has gotten n2 u??
we’ve talked bout this plenty of times
im jus havin a change of heart i think.
he’s my husband, but that doesn’t stop me
this isn’t how u usually act
u told me ‘who cares’ bout Dave
that u loved me above anyone else
i did… well, ive changed my mind.
i don’t think we should do this anymore.
i was jus bout to get a divorce and leave my family for u
u said we’d move to Cali, start a new life together
r u havin memory loss or something?!?!
how could u jus leave Dave like that?
that it? ud leave ur entire family for me.
how he treats me! how he goes out almost every night and comes back drunk. cant stand that bastard anymore
how do u know wat he needs??!?
u told me he always whines to u bout life and u cant stand it!!
y r u acting so weird?!?!
this is ur husband on Tom’s phone…
how in the… how did u get his phone?!?!
we were out gettin drinks. i was ‘whining’ to him i guess according 2 u.
and he got up 2 go 2 the restroom and left his phone on the bar.
then u txted and i recognized ur #...
that’s private info and pretty sure illegal to snoop on another’s phone!!
ur cheating on me!! i think that is worse!!!!!
i know everything… and ur gonna pay…
uv treated me like shit lately!!!
which gives u reason to cheat?!?! wit my bestfriend!!!!
pls pls pls dont hurt him…
we wont have to worry bout him anymore…
who?!?! is this DAVE?!?!? im gonna kill u!!
ur relationship wit tom is over Mary…
wat does that mean?!?! wat did u do to him?!?!
lets jus say i eliminated all the competition…
im callin the cops, getting the kids, and getting out of here!!!
goodbye Dave, im leaving. be gone before u get back
and if i ever see u again, i will have u arrested
u cant escape me!!! i will find u!!!
